data.description: Move in and enjoy your first, second or last home sitting nicely on 3 acres in Chardon.  Gracious large living room and dining room welcomes you with a gas fireplace, custom built mantel and hardwood flooring throughout.  Fully remodeled kitchen in 2023 with all appliances included.  Home boosts a first-floor master with an on-suite half bath, heated three season room and enclosed back porch, two bedrooms upstairs, full unfinished basement, landscaped with multiple outside garden areas, detached two car garage all on a beautiful lot with a creek running through the middle! Make yourself home as you step into the spacious foyer with coat closet and shoe shelf and additional storage behind closet.  First floor master with hardwood floors a half bath and a nice size closet. Second floor has two bedrooms with storage spaces, a hallway closet and full bathroom.  The full unfinished lower level has laundry, storage, recreation and workshop areas.  Outside the house has a wraparound driveway, garden area, fireplace area, a bridge over the creek and a two-car detached garage with a side access door.  Seller is providing a one-year home warranty, all appliances and immediate possession.  Beautiful piece of property!
